{"tid":1473220,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"BNO自救！","createTime":"2019-08-14T19:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T12:55:57.000Z","uid":183824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"000208f2c2121df20a071ecf3f44781cc5fb331f","tid":1473220,"uid":183824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:08:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=6d9800bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n俾BNO持有人予英國國籍！<br />\n香港人互相幫忙，幫得幾多得幾多！<br />\n大家同我簽撚咗份petition佢！<br />\n利申97後冇BNO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822dbc8449e863d26a851c614c05dbd3d526d4db","tid":1473220,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:11:29.000Z","msg":"97後變condom"},{"pid":"789970f7e691d8ccbb55e411dffbdb3daba0dd08","tid":1473220,"uid":226569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:13:58.000Z","msg":"【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=6d9800bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ1 : 簽咗咁多聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> / 英國佬唔會幫我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> /英國佬都唔想收咁多新移民喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />/ 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Q2: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 （ ff住先）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ4: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=6d9800bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"3e53cf010ad3ae5156029c4aeafa16a9ca02a376","tid":1473220,"uid":296928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:18:35.000Z","msg":"唔走。救香港，唔會放棄，除非出解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：有BNO，屋企人諗住走。"},{"pid":"86d5ce04b581728cfa1588279979cd1c15f2c030","tid":1473220,"uid":73293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:30:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">818， 追討黑警濫權!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">818， 正視警黑合作!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXPug1n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXPug1n.jpg&h=448ec9ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4908209870eca394e7492f2429920fe32225fa88","tid":1473220,"uid":299085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T20:18:24.000Z","msg":"對呢個問題我有小小認識，分享下<br />\n1. British nationality law 非常複雜, <a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/British_nationality_law\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FBritish_nationality_law&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=0b7c6b0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/British_nationality_law</a><br />\n簡單講，BC 唔係一定世襲，香港人用居英權拿到BC, 屬於naturalisation。呢種BC 如果想傳下一代，<span style=\"color: red;\">小孩一定要係英國出生</span>。所以現時開始見有住香港有BC，大住肚跑去倫敦生仔，就係因為又唔想離開香港但又想買保險。<br />\n<br />\n2. 呢D咁嘅 Commons committee, 講到好巴閉，都係要嚟做 show, <span style=\"color: red;\">表示佢對人權做左野</span>，跟住記錄在案，其實一錢不值，唔好中計想多左。<br />\n<br />\n3. 點解咁講？有乜數據？聽過 Brexit咪？ 係乜嚟㗎？<br />\nBrexit 就係話<span style=\"color: red;\">英國唔要任何唔係英國嘅人! </span>佢地宜家連一起生活左幾十年，同英國相同血統，文化嘅歐洲都要分離，做乜無啦啦要你D咁遠水路嚟嘅黃種人呀？<br />\n<br />\n4. 仲味信？咁我問你，知唔知 Boris Johnson 係乜水呀？唔知就 google 啦。佢最近選出做首相係因為乜呀？因為佢堅持 brexit 越硬越好，即係話同歐盟越分到冇彎轉越堅。佢點解咁極端都選得出？<span style=\"color: red;\">因為宜家D英國選民潮流興排外呀</span>，咁你諗下英國政府有幾大機會真係歡迎你D香港人呀？<br />\n<br />\n唔係掃興，香港人衹可以靠自己!"},{"pid":"5ef0f196fd0f8a00a0a5858324a6d50c2c8aeec8","tid":1473220,"uid":272795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T23:49:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34939e89612ea8a953701b82ea0e8a9e77740ffd","tid":1473220,"uid":179293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:51:45.000Z","msg":"🇬🇧❤ Support BNO Hong Konger 🙏🏻非常緊急呼籲：英屬香港人簽署！（廣傳）<br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852 / 000000<br />\n<br />\n#簽署 Sign tick ✅ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg0oInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=6d9800bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"c41638ac122ba8a836a159e29708b3487f8a847d","tid":1473220,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"借位推Post唔該<br />\n<br />\n推! 第二次BNO平權聯署<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/QOCwEU\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/QOCwEU</a>"},{"pid":"dc0634f51327fe41c25dd509ef67a26feec9eb8e","tid":1473220,"uid":295889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:55:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正經post冇人推！？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Set deadline再升級係大多手足嘅共識 大家一齊去公投同討下啦 要過5,000正評 民間記者會應該要反映到抗爭者主流意見同策略</span> </span><br />\n冇網絡大軍同P牌不能好評 要靠大家！！<br />\n<br />\n【公投】民間記者會設限825通牒林奠答應訴求（係答應唔係回應！！！）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dEHHFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.